   <body>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCbce45470258d100586b5fed1f18860d2"></a>Refitting the gear selector lever
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15310"> </a>Position the gearbox drum selector fork in the centre of the gear rollers.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15312"> </a>Position the gear selector lever (3) together with control shaft, spring and plate into the chain-side crankcase half.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_033902073.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15317"> </a>Insert the screws (1) and (2) with the spacer (4).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15319"> </a>Temporarily fit gear change lever (or a service lever) and engine pinion and shift to neutral gear.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_032802062.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15324"> </a>Place the tool (A) no. <span class="bold">88713.3334</span> on the gear ratchet.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_034102074.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15332"> </a>Place the tool (A) no. <span class="bold">88713.3334</span> inserting the clutch rod (E) into the tool hole, block the pin (F) of the tool in the gear ratchet pressing with the hand
            in the point (G) (ratchet stroke stop plate) towards the right, as shown in photo.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_034202075.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_034302076.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15342"> </a>In this position, tighten the retaining screw (1) to a torque of 36 Nm (Min. 34 Nm - Max. 38 Nm) and screw (2) to 16 Nm (Min.
            15 Nm - Max. 17 Nm).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/warning.jpg">Warning
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15346"> </a>Make sure that the gear selector lever fixing screws are those indicated in our spare parts catalogue. They must be screws
         of class 12.9 in order to respect the tightening torque indicated above.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15349"> </a>Start tightening the first screw (1), and continue with screw (2).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_034402077.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_034502078.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_034602079.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15358"> </a>Remove service tool no.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15360"> </a>Check that the pin (H) placed on the gear drum is axially to the notch (L) on the gear claw (with gear in neutral).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_034702080.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15365"> </a>With the gearbox in neutral, check that the lever travel is the same when shifting up and down. The same should apply when
            a gear is engaged.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15367"> </a>Operate the gearchange lever and turn the front sprocket at the same time to check that all the gears engage when shifting
            up and down.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15369"> </a>Remove the previously installed lever and sprocket.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15372"> </a>Refit the generator cover and the flywheel/generator unit (<a href="45184.html#DUCe2a16b98259310058919eb60359b4bd2">Refitting the flywheel/generator unit</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15377"> </a>Refit the water pump/radiator pipes (<a href="44926.html#DUC62ddf200250210058a868a10427928d2">Refitting cooling system pipes and unions</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15382"> </a>Refit the pump-cylinder hoses (<a href="45120.html#DUC24353f28257910058ca3f04d994144d2">Refitting the cylinder/piston assembly</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15387"> </a>Refill the cooling system (<a href="77257.html#DUCf34a5aa829f91005800d816ce97b3fd2">Changing the coolant</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15392"> </a>Refit the clutch slave cylinder (<a href="78740.html#DUC1fe52c982b2410058cedd30e2bfae6c4">Refitting the clutch slave cylinder</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15397"> </a>Refit the sprocket cover (<a href="79976.html#DUC6a6ab4402b2410058de4ee3905e05ec4">Refitting the front sprocket</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15402"> </a>Fill the system with engine oil (<a href="77245.html#DUCc57ed0d029f510058c2bed44952c77d2">Changing engine oil and filter cartridge</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15407"> </a>Refit the oil sump guard unit (<a href="78008.html#DUC69eeed302aaa10058bbcf20939ae18d2">Refitting the oil sump guard</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
